<i>noun</i>: 암송 [암ː송], 낭송 [낭ː송], 낭독 [낭ː독] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>암송 [암ː송]</dt><br>
<dd>recitation</dd><br>
<dd>시나 문장 등을 보지 않고 외워 말함.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of repeating a poem or sentence from one's memory, without looking.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>낭송 [낭ː송]</dt><br>
<dd>recitation</dd><br>
<dd>시나 문장 등을 소리 내어 읽음.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of reading out something such as a poem or sentence.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>낭독 [낭ː독]</dt><br>
<dd>recitation</dd><br>
<dd>글을 소리 내어 읽음.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of reading a piece of writing out loud, usually in front of an audience.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>